emuInput.TitMainTitle: Portrait of Helen Phillips posed with hand on hip, in front of scalloped background, in Harris Studio
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 4, 1939, pg. 9, reads: "Representing Smoky City - Lovely Helen Phillips will represent the Pittsburgh Chapter of the Debs About Town, when they meet in New York next week-end. (Photo by Harris)."
